Directed by Jong-bin Yoon

Written by Sung-hui Kwon. Jong-bin Yoon

Cast Ha Jung-woo( Kang In Gu6 episodes, 2022 ). Hwang Jung-min( Jeon Yo Hwan6 episodes, 2022 ). Park Hae-soo( Choi Chang Ho6 episodes, 2022 ). Woo-jin Jo( Byeon Ki Tae6 episodes, 2022 ). Yoo Yeon-Seok( David Park6 episodes, 2022 ). Chu Ja-hyeon( Park Hye-jin6 episodes, 2022 ). Chidi Ajufo( Gallas6 episodes, 2022 ). Fabiony Sylvain( Mercenary 36 episodes, 2022 ). Nubel Feliz Yan( Mercenario 26 episodes, 2022 ). Chang Chen( Chen Zhen5 episodes, 2022 ). Jordan Preston( General / …4 episodes, 2022 ). Daniel C Kennedy( Blue Team Leader3 episodes, 2022 ). Edward Gelhaus( Boss2 episodes, 2022 ). Bryan Larkin( DEA Chief2 episodes, 2022 ). Foster Burden( DEA Agent 12 episodes, 2022 ). Joe Nowell( Brazil Border Guard, Suriname Motor Officer2 episodes, 2022 ). Édgar Vittorino( James1 episode, 2022 ). Christian Larson( DEA Agent1 episode, 2022 ). John D. Michaels( Blue Target Director1 episode, 2022 ). 

Language Korean

Producers Myung Chan Kang

Production Moonlight Film. Perfect Storm Film.

Official site Netflix

Season 1

Episodes 6
